KEEP app.py, assignment8.ipynb, diabetes.csv files in 1 saparate folder

STEP-1 : RUN THE assignment8.ipynb file
STEP-2 : You can see logistic_model.pkl & scaler.pkl file created inside the folder
STEP-3 : go to app.py, open terminal and run this below command
        streamlit run app.py
STEP-4 : You can now view your Streamlit app in your browser. by click the link inside the terminal streamlit webpage opens you can put your values and get your predictions.

thank you


